content:
This is a playtester build which was given an actual name, which is quite rare.
It was mostly intended for multiplayer testing over Net64 and contained a lot of new content later publicly released in 0.7.
There are 17 new areas here which you can see at
https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1HhX6ldAGSTQxWO--DQ28KYCAQeOZw8FzfvuUC8fUG6g/edit?gid=2060005990
